com.itworks.snamp.management

Class AgentManagerBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snamp.AbstractAggregator
      • com.itworks.snamp.core.AbstractPlatformService
        • com.itworks.snamp.management.AbstractAgentManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Aggregator, AgentManager, PlatformPlugin, PlatformService, java.lang.AutoCloseable, net.xeoh.plugins.base.Plugin
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsoleAgentManager

    public abstract class AgentManagerBase
extends AbstractPlatformService
implements AgentManager
    Represents an abstract class for implementing custom SNAMP managers.

    The inherited class must be annotated with PluginImplementation, and have parameterless constructor.

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
